src.description: The source url to display in an iframe
src.description_zh: 要在 iframe 中显示的源 URL

title.description: (Accessibility) Set the native 'title' attribute value of the inner iframe being used
title.description_zh: （辅助功能）设置正在使用的内部 iframe 的原生“title”属性值

fetchpriority.description: Provides a hint of the relative priority to use when fetching the iframe document
fetchpriority.description_zh: 提供提取 iframe 文档时要使用的相对优先级的提示

loading.description: Indicates how the browser should load the iframe
loading.description_zh: 指示浏览器应如何加载 iframe

referrerpolicy.description: Indicates which referrer to send when fetching the frame's resource
referrerpolicy.description_zh: 指示在获取帧资源时要发送的引用
